# agent-stack

AI agent configuration for agentic coding in Cursor. Single stack: Supabase, Better Auth, Hono, tRPC, React, TanStack Router + Query, Shadcn.

Shared across projects via git submodule. Improve a prompt once — every project gets it.

---

## What's Inside

```
agent-stack/
├── agents/
│   ├── planning/                     # Reasoning models — produce documents
│   │   ├── requirements-agent.md     # Dialog → 00-requirements.md
│   │   ├── ux-designer-agent.md      # Dialog → 01-ui-spec.md (conditional)
│   │   ├── test-strategist-agent.md  # → 02-test-spec.md
│   │   ├── orchestrator-agent.md     # → 03-plan.md
│   │   ├── ticket-writer-agent.md    # → tickets/T*.md
│   │   └── reviewer-agent.md         # Final review
│   └── execution/                    # Fast models — produce code
│       ├── db-agent.md
│       ├── storage-agent.md
│       ├── api-agent.md
│       ├── auth-agent.md
│       ├── ui-agent.md
│       ├── test-writer-agent.md      # Unit + integration tests
│       ├── e2e-test-writer-agent.md
│       ├── test-runner-agent.md      # Runs full suite, self-heals E2E
│       └── mutation-tester-agent.md
├── skills/
│   ├── agent-registry.md
│   ├── supabase.md
│   ├── drizzle.md
│   ├── better-auth.md
│   ├── hono.md
│   ├── trpc.md
│   ├── react.md
│   ├── tanstack.md
│   ├── shadcn.md
│   └── typescript.md
├── rules/
│   ├── stack-context.mdc             # Always-on: tech stack, auth, testing
│   └── intent-routing.mdc            # Classify: full feature / continue / quick fix / review
├── hooks/
│   ├── cursor/
│   │   ├── event-logger.js
│   │   ├── block-dangerous-commands.js
│   │   └── post-tool-use-check.js
│   └── git/
│       └── commit-msg-append-review.sh
├── commands/
│   └── commit.md
└── README
```

---

## 5-Phase Pipeline

| Phase | Agents | Output |
|-------|--------|--------|
| **0. Discovery** | requirements-agent, ux-designer-agent*, test-strategist-agent | 00-requirements.md, 01-ui-spec.md, 02-test-spec.md |
| **1. Planning** | orchestrator-agent, ticket-writer-agent | 03-plan.md, tickets/T*.md |
| **2. Execution** | test-writer-agent, e2e-test-writer-agent, db-agent, storage-agent, api-agent, auth-agent, ui-agent | Code files |
| **3. Testing** | test-runner-agent, mutation-tester-agent | Test results, fixes |
| **4. Review** | reviewer-agent | Review appended to plan, commit snippet |

*ux-designer-agent runs only when the feature has UI.

**Artifact flow:**

```
00-requirements.md  ← requirements-agent (dialog)
01-ui-spec.md      ← ux-designer-agent (dialog, conditional)
02-test-spec.md    ← test-strategist-agent

         ↓ all 3 feed into

03-plan.md         ← orchestrator-agent

         ↓ plan feeds into

tickets/T01-*.md, T02-*.md, ...  ← ticket-writer-agent

         ↓ each ticket feeds its execution agent
```

---

